long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension assists with providing the browser with secure identity tokens when making requests to secure Google Cloud Run services where an identity token is required.  The extension communicates with a local CLI server on your system to periodically retrieve new tokens.  This automates the process and eliminates the need to manually copy tokens, as is done in extensions like ModHeaders.
